'''美國維珍尼亞州電視直播槍擊案'''是一起發生於[[美國東部|美國東部]][[夏令時間|夏令時間]]2015年8月26日的[[命案|命案]]。事件中，[[CBS_(电视网)|CBS]]旗下的{{link-en|WDBJ電視台|WDBJ}}24歲的[[記者|記者]]'''艾莉森·帕克'''（'''Alison Parker'''）和27歲的[[攝影記者|攝影記者]]'''亞當·沃德'''（'''Adam Ward'''）在美國[[維珍尼亞州|維珍尼亞州]]{{link-en|莫尼塔|Moneta, Virginia}}{{link-en|史密斯山湖|Smith Mountain Lake}}附近進行電視新聞直播採訪時被一名槍手射殺<ref name="wdbj7_20150826">{{cite web|url=http://www.wdbj7.com/news/local/law-enforcement-investigating-incident-at-bridgewater-plaza/34923086 |title=Two WDBJ7 employees killed in attack at Bridgewater Plaza |website=WDBJ7 |date=2015-08-26 |accessdate=2015-08-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150826131524/http://www.wdbj7.com/news/local/law-enforcement-investigating-incident-at-bridgewater-plaza/34923086 |archivedate=2015-08-26 }}</ref>。史密斯山湖商會的維基·加德納（Vickie Gardner）是當時的受訪者，她也在事件中遭到槍擊，但倖免於難<ref name=WPost.Head>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/local/third-victim-in-virginia-shooting-is-head-of-local-chamber-of-commerce/2015/08/26/1ad878a4-4c03-11e5-bfb9-9736d04fc8e4_story.html|title=Shooting victim Vicki Gardner is head of local chamber of commerce|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26|first=Antonio|last=Olivo}}</ref><ref name=Heavy.Facts/>；帕克和沃德則當場身亡，他們分別是1992年以來美國第七、八位在工作期間被殺害的記者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2015/08/26/virginia-journalists-shot-were-the-seventh-and-eighth-killed-in-the-u-s-since-1992/|title=Virginia journalists shot were the seventh and eighth killed in the U.S. since 1992|work=華盛頓郵報|date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26|first=Mark|last=Berman}}</ref>。

槍手被證實是兩年之前被解僱的WDBJ前記者、41歲男子韋斯特·李·弗萊納根〔Vester Lee Flanagan II，曾使用[[藝名|藝名]]布萊斯·威廉姆斯（Bryce Williams）〕<ref name="cnn_20150826">{{cite web| url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/08/26/us/virginia-shooting-wdbj/index.html| title=Virginia TV reporter, photographer killed in shooting during live interview| website=[[CNN|CNN]]| date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26| first=Eliott C.| last=McLaughlin}}</ref><ref name="nytimes_20150826">{{cite web| url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/27/us/wdbj7-virginia-journalists-shot-during-live-broadcast.html| title=Virginia TV Reporter and Photographer Shot During Live Broadcast| website=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]| date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26| first1=Katie| last1=Rogers| first2=Alan| last2=Blinder}}</ref><ref name="time_20150826">{{cite web| url=http://time.com/4011147/wdbj7-virginia-shooting/| title=Photographer and Reporter Killed During Live Broadcast| website=[[時代週刊|時代週刊]]| date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26| first=Justin| last=Worland}}</ref><ref name="usatoday_20150826">{{cite web| url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/08/26/reports-two-dead-virginia-shooting-live-tv/32391633/| title=Virginia reporter, photographer killed on live TV| first=John| last=Bacon| date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26| website=[[今日美國|今日美國]]}}</ref>。經過警方近五個小時的追捕之後，弗萊納根在追車期間向自己開槍，之後在醫院身亡<ref name="usatoday_20150826"/><ref name=USAToday.Angered/>。

==槍擊經過==
事發時，帕克和沃德位於[[維珍尼亞州|維珍尼亞州]]{{link-en|莫尼塔|Moneta, Virginia}}的水橋廣場，正在與加德納進行一場關於{{link-en|史密斯山湖|Smith Mountain Lake}}五十周年紀念的採訪。槍擊發生在早上6時45分，當時這段採訪進行到一半，且正在WDBJ的早間新聞節目「''Mornin{{'}}''」直播。電視畫面顯示，帕克進行採訪時，現場突然傳來至少八聲槍響，並伴有尖叫聲。沃德手持的攝像機也隨之墜落在地，並短暫地捕捉到弗萊納根手持槍支的畫面。緊接著直播畫面被切換回演播室主播金伯利·麥布魯姆（Kimberly McBroom），她看起來並不能確定之前發生了什麽。據她其後稱，她當時以為現場的聲音是汽車逆火爆鳴，或是來自遠處的槍響<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.9news.com.au/world/2015/08/27/15/03/news-anchor-thought-car-backfired-after-colleagues-murdered-on-air|title=News anchor thought car backfired when gunman shot colleagues on air|work=Ninemsn|date=2015-08-27|accessdate=2015-08-27}}</ref>。槍擊發生一段時間後，艾莉森·帕克和亞當·沃德被確認在槍擊中身亡，而加德納背部中槍。她之後被送往醫院接受手術，並倖免於難<ref name="msnbc_20150826">{{cite web| url=http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/reporter-and-cameraman-killed-during-live-broadcast| title=Reporter and cameraman killed during live broadcast| first=Anna| last= Brand| date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26| website=[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]}}</ref><ref name="ap.org">{{cite web|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/379b43ac8db44392a594ee48ed889a84/manager-2-virginia-tv-station-workers-fatally-shot-air|title=Fired reporter kills 2 former co-workers on live TV|work=[[美聯社|美聯社]]|first=Steve|last=Helber|first2=Pam|last2=Ramsey|first3=Jonathan|last3=Drew|date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26}}</ref>。槍擊時共發射了十五槍<ref name=Heavy.Facts/>。

WDBJ新聞編輯室的員工在事發後意識到槍手可能是弗萊納根，並將信息提供給了-{zh-cn:县;zh-tw:郡;zh-hk:縣}-警長<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/virginia-tv-shooting/virginia-tv-shooting-chilling-image-alerted-station-killer-vester-flanagan-n416826|title=Virginia TV Shooting: Chilling Image Alerted Station to Killer Vester Flanagan|work=[[全國廣播公司|NBC]]|first=Erin|last=Mcclam|date=2015-08-27|accessdate=2015-08-27}}</ref>。弗萊納根8時23分向[[ABC新闻|ABC]]發送了一份傳真，並在10時後不久又打了電話，坦承自己作案<ref name=Jack/>。在接下來的追捕過程中，當局透過追蹤弗萊納根的手機訊號將其定位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fox8.com/2015/08/26/virginia-gunman-details-grievances-in-lengthy-suicide-note-references-charleston-church-shooting/|title=Virginia gunman details grievances in lengthy 'suicide note,' references Charleston church shooting|work=fox8|date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26}}</ref>。弗萊納根在{{link-en|羅阿諾克-布萊克斯堡地區機場|Roanoke–Blacksburg Regional Airport}}丟棄了他的[[福特野馬|福特野馬]]跑車，並駕駛租來的[[雪佛蘭|雪佛蘭]]轎車，沿[[66号州际公路|66号州际公路]]向東逃離。在[[福基爾縣_(維吉尼亞州)|-{zh-hk:福基爾縣;zh-tw:福基爾郡;zh-cn:福基尔县}-]]，一名州警車輛上的自動車牌讀取器於11時20分識別出了這輛轎車，該州警隨後打電話請求增援，並嘗試攔截弗萊納根，但其加速逃走。在追逐不到兩英里後，弗萊納根的車衝出公路，撞上路堤。他在車內被發現時身上帶有槍傷<ref name=USAToday.Angered/>，顯然是在駕車期間造成的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/27/us/wdbj7-virginia-journalists-shot-during-live-broadcast.html?_r=0|title=Suspect in Virginia Shooting of News Team Commits Suicide|work=The New York Times|date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26|first=Hawes|last=Spencer|first2=Katie|last2=Rogers|first3=Alan|last3=Blinder|first4=Richard|last4=Pérez-Peña}}</ref>。他迅速被用飛機送往[[福爾斯徹奇_(維吉尼亞州)|-{zh-hk:福爾斯徹奇;zh-tw:福爾斯徹奇;zh-cn:佛尔斯彻赤}-]]的一家醫院，但於下午1時26分被宣佈死亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/suspect-air-shooting-dead-inflicted-wound/story?id=33327920|title=Suspect in On-Air Shooting Dies From Self-Inflicted Wound|work=ABC|date=2015-08-26|first=Meghan|last=Keneally| accessdate=2015-08-26}}</ref><ref name=WPost.Slaying>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/local/wp/2015/08/26/tv-camera-crew-caught-in-active-shooter-situation-in-southwest-virginia/|title=Suspect in slaying of two TV station employees in SW Virginia shoots himself and dies|work=華盛頓郵報|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-08-26|first=Dana|last=Hedgpeth|first2=Justin|last2=Jouvenal}}</ref>。

==受害者==
*'''艾莉森·帕克'''（1991年8月19日－2015年8月26日）在維珍尼亞州[[马丁斯维尔_(弗吉尼亚州)|马丁斯维尔]]長大，先後在該州的{{link-en|帕特里克亨利社區大學|Patrick Henry Community College}}和[[詹姆斯麦迪逊大学|詹姆斯麦迪逊大学]]就讀。2012年在[[北卡羅萊納州|北卡羅萊納州]]以WDBJ實習生身份工作，2014年獲該電視台僱用，任「''Mornin{{'}}''」的記者<ref name="cnn_20150826"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wdbj7.com/news/local/a-look-at-the-lives-of-wdbj7s-alison-parker-and-adam-ward/34929588|title=A look at the lives of WDBJ7's Alison Parker and Adam Ward|work=WDBJ7|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-08-26|first=Joe|last=Dashiell|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828050405/http://www.wdbj7.com/news/local/a-look-at-the-lives-of-wdbj7s-alison-parker-and-adam-ward/34929588|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>。遇害前，帕克剛剛開始與她的男友、WDBJ主播克里斯·赫斯特（Chris Hurst）同居<ref name="wtop_20150826">{{cite web| url=http://liveblogwp.wtop.com/Event/Va_reporter_cameraman_shot_killed_during_live_shot| title=Va. reporter, cameraman shot, killed during live interview| date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26| website={{link-en|WTOP|WTOP-FM}}| first1=Amanda| last1=Iacone| first2=Neal| last2=Augenstein| first3=Marcus J.| last3=Moore| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150826151327/http://liveblogwp.wtop.com/Event/Va_reporter_cameraman_shot_killed_during_live_shot| archivedate=2015年8月26日| df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/08/26/alison-parker-adam-ward-wdbj7-virginia-tv-journalists-dead/32396463/|title=Virginia TV journalists Alison Parker and Adam Ward shot dead: Here's what we know|first=Christine|last= Rushton| work = 今日美國 | date=2015-08-26| accessdate=2015-08-26}}</ref>。她被槍擊後當場身亡。
*'''亞當·沃德'''（1988年－2015年8月26日）在維珍尼亞州[[塞勒姆_(維吉尼亞州)|塞勒姆]]長大，2011年畢業於[[弗吉尼亚理工学院暨州立大学|弗吉尼亚理工学院]]，同年七月加入WDBJ工作直至槍擊案發生<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wtvr.com/2015/08/26/wdbj-reporter-alison-parker-photographer-adam-ward-hailed-by-colleagues-friends/|title=WDBJ reporter Alison Parker, photographer Adam Ward hailed by colleagues, friends|work={{link-en|WTVR|WTVR-TV}}|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-08-26|author1= CNN Wire|author2=Norwood, Jasmine}}</ref>。他已經與WDBJ製片人梅麗莎·奧特（Melissa Ott）訂婚<ref name="wtop_20150826"/>。他也當場身亡。
*'''維基·加德納'''出生於[[紐約州|紐約州]]{{link-en|尤寧斯普林斯 (紐約州)|Union Springs, New York|尤寧斯普林斯}}，事發時61歲，是史密斯山湖商會的主管，也是槍擊時的受訪者。她背部中彈但得以生還，經手術後情況穩定<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.roanoke.com/news/crime/bedford_county/two-wdbj-journalists-dead-after-shooting-at-smith-mountain-lake/article_67c09161-0109-5228-a554-0d14ffc56d51.html|title=State police: Shooting suspect in 'very critical condition' after shooting himself|work={{link-en|羅諾克時報|The Roanoke Times}}|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-08-26|first=Neil |last=Harvey}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/local/third-victim-in-virginia-shooting-is-head-of-local-chamber-of-commerce/2015/08/26/1ad878a4-4c03-11e5-bfb9-9736d04fc8e4_story.html|title=Shooting victim Vicki Gardner is head of local chamber of commerce|first=Antonio |last=Olivo|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-08-26|work=華盛頓郵報}}</ref><ref name=Heavy.Facts/>。

